		(uuid "0890869d-9118-4542-b315-10ff61c750eb")
	)
	(text_box "Since the LiPo battery voltage can drop below the desired system voltage of 3.3V and the input voltage can be as high as 5V, it is recommended to use a buck-boost regulator.\n\nThere is also a significant amount of capacitance on the output rail, so it is recommended to use a regulator with soft-start functionality."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 133.35 63.5 0)
		(size 162.56 38.1)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width -0.0001)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
			(type none)
		)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.54 2.54)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "1f388145-4b2d-4d77-a834-1574ae040178")
	)
	(text_box "For testing and measurement purposes, provide the following:\n- LED indicators to display the states of the voltage rails\n- The ability to easily perform current measurements\n- Test points to verify voltage rail levels"
